PDL::Drawing::Prima - a PDL interface to the Prima drawing commands.

This provides the low-level (C-based) drawing commands that thread over PDL 
arguments. It can be used to quickly draw a large variety of objects using PDL 
threading.

Author: David Mertens <dcmertens.perl.csharp@gmail.com>

Note that my email is intentionally obfuscated. Knowing that I am a
Perl programmer, you can probably remove the part that does not belong.
